        <p>
          If you have a private issue, please email 
          us at <a href="mailto:support@omniscope.io">support@omniscope.io</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          For public issues, or to start a discussion, please feel free to 
          <a href="https://github.com/omniscopeio/huginn/issues" target="_blank">open an issue on Omniscope's fork of Huginn</a>
        </p>
        <h2>Contributing</h2>
        <p>
          We pull in the changes from the open source project pretty regularly.
          If you'd like to add new features in the form of a pull request, 
          or help address other developers concerns, great!
          The <a href="https://github.com/cantino/huginn" target="_blank">Huginn source repo is here on Github</a>.
        </p>
